<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>بَاطِلَة وَفِي الْقَدِيم مَوْقُوفَة<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>بِنَاء على صِحَة وقف الْعُقُود<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>وعَلى الْأَقْوَال<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>من زَوَال ملكه أَو وَقفه أَو بَقَائِهِ<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>يَجْعَل مَاله مَعَ عدل<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
